<html
  <head>
      <title>$i18n.getText("admin_helper.admin.label")</title>
      <meta name="decorator" content="atl.admin"/>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div id="aui-message-bar"></div>
    <h1>Select the backup Zip you want to upload</h1>
    <br>
    <p>This Section is used to Reimport Hardware Backups. The Backup must be a singe Zip file of the follwoing structure:</p>
    <ul>
        <li>device.JSON</li>
        <li>device.JSON</li>
        <li>device.JSON</li>
        <li>device.JSON</li>
        <li>device.JSON</li>
    </ul> <br>
    <p>If the given Backup does not include the files described above, the backup wil be rejected.</p>
    <form class="aui" method="POST" enctype="multipart/form-data" id="upload-form">
        <fieldset>
            <div class="field-group">
                <input class="upfile" type="file" name="upload_field" id="upload-field"/>
            </div>
            <div class="field-group">
                <input type="button" value="Submit" class="aui-button aui-button-primary" id="post-inputs">
            </div>
        </fieldset>
    </form>
  </body>
</html>